title: SHANY 180 Color Eyeshadow Palette (180 Color Eyeshadow Palette, United Colors of SHANY, Neon Frenzy, Limited), 6.25 Ounce
description: This palette is makeup artist dreams come true. 180 highly pigmented eye shadows in every color and texture to create exciting over the top looks. This case comes with neutral, warm and cool tones. In both matte and shimmer textures. Go from the office to a night on the town with this wide variety of hues. Neutral colors can be used at work or during the day for a softer look. If you want to stand out in crowd then use the bold bright and vibrant colors in different and funky combos. Use alone or numerous hues for a color explosion on your eyes. Also comes with 12 double effect shadows. Press a flat shadow brush on these colors instead of blending them to create a speckled effect on the eyes. The possibilities are endless so let your imagination run wild.

title: 20 Pairs Soft Synthetic Fiber False Eyelashes with Glue Hr133
Ben Nye Luxury Powders - Banana 1.5oz
description:
Formerly known as Visage Poudre Luxury Powders, these ultra-neutral powders provide superior matte and subtle finishing. Often compared to French powders with silky-fine textures. the Ben Nye Bella line of powders are translucent with just a hint of color. Please Note: This product does NOT come with a seal! 
Please note: Powders may settle and compress during shipping and some bottles may appear to be partially empty. Shaking the product vigorously will decompress the powder and return it to its original state.
